{"tid":1660268,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一如所料 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-10-17T12:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T12:07:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d3a119e542cf6e957cacb72767b57f4a2d8cc1","tid":1660268,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:00:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191017/20788096/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F20788096%2F&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaATBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=0f6c57a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F20788096%2F&h=74304000\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191017/20788096/</a><br />\n<br />\n一如所料 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191017/large/1571218016_01c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191017%2Flarge%2F1571218016_01c5.jpg&h=52ea0073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭月娥政權十月三日頒佈《禁止蒙面規例》，市民岑敖暉、郭卓堅二人，以及郭榮鏗等二十四位立法會民主派議員，先後訴諸法庭，或以民權為言，或以立法權為言，求法庭以臨時禁制令阻規例實施，法官林雲浩則一如所料拒絕，只答應十月下旬審訊決定《禁止蒙面規例》之頒布有無違憲。郭榮鏗說：「法官同意在短短十多日之後開審，顯然認為當局有違憲之嫌。」<br />\n<br />\n其實審訊結果可以預卜，《人民日報》十月五日頭版《禁止蒙面，止暴制亂》一文已有判詞，說鄭政府所為「合法合情合理」。大家切勿抱任何幻想。<br />\n<br />\n宋朝大儒周敦頤曾任南安軍司理參軍，見有囚徒法不當死，但轉運使王逵欲處以極刑。王逵性情兇悍，屬下只有周敦頤一人敢提異議，王逵不聽，周敦頤就放下手版，要辭官歸去，歎道：「如此尚可仕乎！殺人以媚人，吾不為也。」王逵感動，那囚徒於是得免（《宋史》卷四二七）。舊中國歷朝都有這樣維護法律不惜辭職的官員。<br />\n<br />\n今天，香港司法界高層信譽最著者，應推終審法院前首席法官李國能。但是，一九九九年中共無視終審法院，悍然推翻其吳嘉玲案判決，李國能與終審法院其他四名常任法官「考慮辭職抗議」，結果辭職抗議者一個都沒有。畢竟棧豆甚甘，殊堪戀也。新香港從來未見有一位法官懂得「如此尚可仕乎」的道理，於是我們的法治一如所料。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"9e6cc24daa6772464c1c3bfda95271c148ea7f6f","tid":1660268,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"509d24522502446221a9e83906858531abe91be4","tid":1660268,"uid":183834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCJsuqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCJsuqC.jpg&h=cfa72ca9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}